name: Oliver Patterson
summary:
Oliver Patterson is a 32-year-old Software Engineer living in Los Angeles but originally from San Francisco. He is 6'2", a graduate of the University of California, Berkeley, and works in the technology industry. He speaks two languages: English and Spanish. His key values are hard work, honesty, and kindness. 

In his free time, Oliver enjoys traveling, hiking, reading, and gaming. While he does not adhere to any particular religious beliefs, he leans towards liberal politics. 

He is currently looking for a life partner in a monogamous relationship. Describing himself as an agnostic, straight, white Caucasian man, he does not have children but hopes to in the future. He doesn't own any pets yet and his zodiac sign is Gemini. 

Oliver identifies as an INTJ personality type, enjoys an active lifestyle, and sometimes drinks alcohol but does not smoke or use marijuana or other drugs. 

As for his partner preferences, he is seeking a straight woman aged between 26-35 who does not smoke, partakes in alcohol occasionally, does not use marijuana or other drugs, and has an active lifestyle. She should ideally not have children yet but desire them in the future.
